	['Zombie Cleansing']={
		['I am Corpus and you are a wretched speciman, YES! You will do nicely, It has become overcrowded in this town and it is getting harder to find a empty grave. Can you help me get rid of some of the filthy zombies investing my graves, 5 should be enough to guarantee me a resting space.']=8001,
