	['The Battle for Arathi Basin!']={
		['$N, the battle for Arathi Basin is a battle for resources and territory.  Key points in the area must be held and operated in order to supply our forces with much needed raw materials and supplies.  I charge you to assault the points farthest from our Arathi Basin base.\n\nAssault the farm, the mine, the lumber mill and the blacksmith when they are controlled by the enemy.  Find the enemy\'s banner and rip it from its flag post!\n\nWhen you have done this to all four points, return to me.']=8105,
		['As you no doubt have heard, the League of Arathor is sending large numbers of troops into Arathi Basin.  Eager for food and supplies, these Alliance fools are intent to take and control the rich resources there.  We must show them that Arathi will never again be a home for humans!\n\nGo to Arathi Basin and assault the mine, the lumber mill, the blacksmith and the stables.  Pull down the enemies\' banners, declaring those territories for the Horde.\n\nGo, $N.  Report back to me when this task is complete.']=8120,
		['As you no doubt have heard, the League of Arathor is sending large numbers of troops into Arathi Basin.  Eager for food and supplies, these Alliance fools are intent to take and control the rich resources there.  We must show them that Arathi will never again be a home for humans!\n\nGo to Arathi Basin and assault the mine, the lumber mill, the blacksmith and the stables.  Pull down the enemies\' banners, declaring those territories for the Horde.\n\nGo, $N.  Report back to me when this task is complete.']=8169,
		['As you no doubt have heard, the League of Arathor is sending large numbers of troops into Arathi Basin.  Eager for food and supplies, these Alliance fools are intent to take and control the rich resources there.  We must show them that Arathi will never again be a home for humans!\n\nGo to Arathi Basin and assault the mine, the lumber mill, the blacksmith and the stables.  Pull down the enemies\' banners, declaring those territories for the Horde.\n\nGo, $N.  Report back to me when this task is complete.']=8170,
		['As you no doubt have heard, the League of Arathor is sending large numbers of troops into Arathi Basin.  Eager for food and supplies, these Alliance fools are intent to take and control the rich resources there.  We must show them that Arathi will never again be a home for humans!\n\nGo to Arathi Basin and assault the mine, the lumber mill, the blacksmith and the stables.  Pull down the enemies\' banners, declaring those territories for the Horde.\n\nGo, $N.  Report back to me when this task is complete.']=8171,
