	['Shadows of Doom']={
		['After you bring down the defenses of the Scourge summoning circles that have appeared in the zones under attack, you will be able to confront the acolytes who protect them.\n\nIn truth, these are not men. They are shadows, some of the Lich King\'s most frightening creatures. They can be revealed using the necrotic runes they carry, and then destroyed with magic or strength of arms.']=9085,
	},
	['Dreamwalker Tunic']={
		['Many heroes fell in the last war and many continue to perish at the hands of the Scourge to this day. From the corpses of the fallen, the armor is stripped and taken back to Naxxramas to be used for unknown purposes.\n\nRecover the desecrated armor and wartorn armor scraps and supply to me the other material components I require and I will craft Dreamwalker armor.']=9086,
