	['Robe of Faith']={
		['<Father Montoy makes some strange gestures in the air in front of you.>\n\nBlessed $g boy:girl;, have you found the vestments of the fallen? The poor souls whose last breaths were taken on the field of battle - stripped of everything including their dignity.\n\nBring me the desecrated remnants of the departed along with reagents of purification and you shall know faith.']=9111,
